procfs: do not list TID 0 in /proc/<pid>/task

If a task exits concurrently, task_pid_nr_ns may return 0.

[akpm@linux-foundation.org: coding style tweaks]
[adobriyan@gmail.com: test that /proc/*/task doesn't contain "0"]
